in Point Pleasant today.

807
01:26:49,701 --> 01:26:52,495
Now, I want you to go down there...

808
01:26:52,579 --> 01:26:54,789
and meet him at the airport.

809
01:26:56,833 --> 01:26:59,169
You listening?

810
01:26:59,252 --> 01:27:01,754
Yeah, McCal I...
