for, say, 10 or 15 minutes.

893
01:34:44,968 --> 01:34:47,971
- I'm sorry. Can I call you back?
- No, you can't.

894
01:34:49,139 --> 01:34:51,891
- I booked you a flight.
- What?

895
01:34:51,975 --> 01:34:54,936
It leaves Dulles
for Columbus, Ohio at 1:45.

896
01:34:57,272 --> 01:35:01,568
